elements.name: As a user I edit the title and description of the site

steps.name: I set scenario "Manage_settings_edit_title_description" and version app "<VERSION>"
I enter "<USER>" into input field having id "ember8"
I enter "<PASSWORD>" into input field having id "ember10"
I click on element having id "ember12"
I click on element having xpath "(//a[@class='ember-view'])[8]"
I click on element having xpath "(//button[@class='gh-btn'])[1]"
I enter "New Title Site" into input field having xpath "(//input[@class='ember-text-field gh-input ember-view'])[1]"
I enter "New Description Site" into input field having xpath "(//input[@class='ember-text-field gh-input ember-view'])[2]"
I click on element having xpath "//button[@class='gh-btn gh-btn-blue gh-btn-icon ember-view']"
I verify "New Title Site" into input field having xpath "(//input[@class='ember-text-field gh-input ember-view'])[1]"
I verify "New Description" into input field having xpath "(//input[@class='ember-text-field gh-input ember-view'])[2]"
